<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Advanced Layout Systems</title>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <style>
        /* Advanced CSS Variables & Root Definitions */
        :root {
            --primary-brand: #4f46e5;
            --secondary-brand: #06b6d4;
            --neutral-dark: #1f2937;
            --neutral-light: #f9fafb;
            --transition-smooth: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        /* CSS Grid System Layout Architecture */.custom-grid-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Modern Product Card with Custom Interactions & Pseudo-classes */.interactive-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }.interactive-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-brand), var(--secondary-brand));
        }.interactive-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Micro-interaction Button with CSS Keyframes Animation */.animated-action-btn {
            background-color: var(--primary-brand);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }.animated-action-btn:hover {
            animation: pulse-glow 1.5s infinite;
            background-color: #4338ca;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-glow {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.7); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 12px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(79, 70, 229, 0); }
        }

        /* Responsive Breakpoint Layout Adjustments via Media Queries */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {.custom-grid-container {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-900 font-sans">

    <header class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200 sticky top-0 z-50 px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
        <span class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-indigo-600">DesignSyllabus Platform</span>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 font-medium">
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition">Grid Component</a>
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition">Tailwind Sandbox</a>
            <a href="#" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-indigo-600 transition">Bootstrap Integration</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
        
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">CSS Grid & Micro-interactions Module</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">This section demonstrates structural layout parameters using CSS custom variables, precise pseudo-elements, and keyframe loading animations.</p>
            
            <div class="custom-grid-container">
                <div class="interactive-card">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Module 22</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2 mb-3">CSS Grid Engine</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">Build responsive grid structures that automatically calculate optimal column distributions based on screen size.</p>
                    <button class="animated-action-btn">Initialize Flow</button>
                </div>

                <div class="interactive-card">
                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-cyan-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Module 12</span>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mt-2 mb-3">Animation Systems</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-6">Implement performance-focused hardware-accelerated transforms to handle interactive hover states cleanly.</p>
                    <button class="animated-action-btn">Trigger State</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16 bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-gray-800">Tailwind Utility Compilation Hub</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">Renders responsive UI elements using standalone padding, flex layout, and color utility classes instead of traditional internal stylesheets.</p>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                <div class="flex-1 p-6 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 border border-indigo-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-indigo-900 mb-2">Flexible Content Card</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-indigo-700">This container automatically reflows its children horizontally on tablets and larger viewports, while stacking columns vertically on mobile targets.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 p-6 rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-cyan-900 mb-2">Rapid Prototyping Mode</h4>
                    <p class="text-sm text-cyan-700">Utility structures make interface iterations fast by moving styling rules directly into standard component layout tags.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="container-fluid bg-dark text-white rounded-3 p-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <h2 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Bootstrap Grid Framework Core</h2>
                    <p class="lead text-muted">Leverages standard 12-column flexbox container logic, built-in layout rows, and responsive spacing modifiers for fast layout scaffolding.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-end">
                    <div class="btn-group" role="group">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 me-2">Primary Action</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-4">Secondary Action</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 text-center py-12 border-t border-gray-800 mt-20">
        <p class="text-sm">Comprehensive Assignment Complete Compilation Directory • Web Architecture Syllabus 2026</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
